SOLD

Why not you ask?

For many reasons but to name a few… I absolutely love this art form. I was a hairdresser 💇‍♀️ for many many years so art has always been my career choice. I now create dolls full time and have since 2016ish. I also love this community, I have met many wonderful people through the years in the reborn community. I also love the flexibility it gives me. It’s nice to work from home. As many of you know I had a surgery injury in 2018 and then developed an autoimmune disease so having the flexibility in my schedule has been wonderful for me. I am able to make my own schedule and rest when I need to. I’ve been known to take a quick break and just lay on the floor til my pain subsides 🤪 lol, I probably couldn’t do that if I was still working in a salon. I wouldn’t be able to do any of this without my wonderful customers which is another reason I’ll never get sick of this, I have the best customers in the world! ❤️❤️❤️
